  "body": "We should be properly handling forked chain block with the following:\r\n```\r\nIf we receive bad blocks:\r\n\tdiscard it/ do not save it in db\r\nIf we receive blocks from forked chain:\r\n\tupdate attestations targets, save it in the db because the block can be head again\r\nelse:\r\n\tprocess the block \r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nIssue today:\r\n1.) we save attestation targets even though the block is bad (bad signature/bad data)\r\n2.) we don't handle receiving blocks from forked chain",
